data.description: This ranch home situated on a corner lot with fenced in backyard is perfect for entertaining. After entering through the breezeway, step into the newly updated kitchen and dining area and be ready to enjoy this space for years to come. The updated appliances and flooring give the kitchen a fresh look. The dining area opens to the family room where you can enjoy relaxing evenings or your morning coffee. The living room features a fireplace that will keep you warm and cozy during the long winter months. As you head back to the basement you will be amazed at how much space you have! Bring your ideas and transform the space into the perfect gameroom, mancave, bar, possible in-law suite, workout area, kids play area, the list goes on! There is an additional room in the basement that could be used as a workshop, 200-amp electrical panel can be found there. New boiler system internals as well. Home is being sold As-Is.
